---
---
<section
  id="about"
  class="py-24"
  style="
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 50%, rgba(232,121,249,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #2d0a4a 0%, #1a0533 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(196,181,253,0.08);
  "
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Mascot -->
      <div>
        <img
          src="/images/mascot.png"
          alt="Kenzie"
          class="w-full max-w-sm md:max-w-full"
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 28px rgba(244,114,182,0.32)) drop-shadow(0 12px 40px rgba(139,92,246,0.28));"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-[0.7rem] font-extrabold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-3" style="color:#e879f9;">✦ The Maker ✦</p>

        <span class="font-script block leading-none" style="font-size:2.4rem; color:#e879f9; text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(232,121,249,0.4);">Hi, I'm</span>
        <span class="font-black tracking-widest text-white block" style="font-size:2.8rem; margin-top:-0.4rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">KENZIE! 👋</span>

        <p class="text-white/55 text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I started making candles when I was 13, and I haven't been able to stop since! There's something so magical about blending scents and watching a blank jar transform into something beautiful.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Every Kenzie's Kandle is hand-poured in small batches using 100% soy wax and premium fragrance oils. I put so much love into each one — I hope they bring a little magic to your space. 💜
        </p>

        <a href="#contact" class="glow-btn inline-block text-white font-bold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-base">
          Say Hello 💌
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
